    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In case someone need it. You can use</p>\n<pre><code>Document.get().getElementById(&quot;counter&quot;).getPropertyString(&quot;value&quot;)\n</code></pre>\n"
